INSERT INTO
                l1_batches (
                    number,
                    timestamp,
                    l1_gas_price,
                    l2_fair_gas_price,
                    fair_pubdata_price,
                    l1_tx_count,
                    l2_tx_count,
                    bloom,
                    priority_ops_onchain_data,
                    initial_bootloader_heap_content,
                    used_contract_hashes,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    is_sealed
                )
            VALUES
                (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    0,
                    0,
                    ''::bytea,
                    '{}'::bytea[],
                    '{}'::jsonb,
                    '{}'::jsonb,
                    NOW(),
                    NOW(),
                    FALSE
                )
